For Linux distros without gsmlib (eg: CentOS):

In the directory gsmlib-1.10-patched-13ubuntu is the source for gsmlib
as patched by Ubuntu for modern compilers:

	./configure
	make
	make install

Debian 12 notes:
- Install build deps (example): `apt-get install build-essential libtool-bin gettext`
- Then run the same `./configure && make && make install`.
